This is my first surf map i no there is a few bugs but i couldnt seem to fix them. This was meant to be a private map for my server but i decided to release it.


YOU MUST HAVE MY PERMISSION FOR RE RELEASE!

(_surf motion1 has not been ported to CS:GO by me, so I don't have a download link to it. You should go to CGN surf servers if you want to play it, because as far as I know they are the ones that ported it_).

The map has been edited again to make it a bit easier, the purpose of this map was t4-t5 but it turned out t6 before, now it should be fine. The map has been renamed to surf_motion1 as I will propably create surf_motion2 in the future.

So, this is a linear surf map, surfing it takes about 1 minute.

Things that have been made in this version:
#Green "stage"
- Nothing has been changed,

#Blue "stage"
- Made the spin a bit easier,
- Replaced the first bhop parts with ramps,
- Made the last bhop part easier to do on high ping,

#Yellow "stage"
- Made the first jump easier,
- Fixed the boost near the end so you can have more control on the ramp,

#White "stage"
- Nothing has been changed,

#Orange "stage"
- The whole stage has been remade (excluding the first ramp),

#Red "stage"
- Everything has been remade until the first spin,
- Made the ending easier (bigger gaps between the "columns",
this is my  first map.

This is a surf map i made quite a while ago for me and my brother, never really got around to uploading it. so... here it is :D surf_MorningGlory. its a medium sized surf map which would be a good map with more players on i think, which is why im uploading it. there are a good few secrets on it too ;D i think it's 100% done now, minus the textures, sooooo. enjoy :D

This is a skill surf map with 6 stages.
The stages aren't very long, but hard (at least I hope so ;)).
There are 2 jails, one of them is only available, if someone finishes the map.
If all people fail, they get teleported in the other jail (see last picture) and get weapons, depending on the stage where they failed at.

Thanks to:

xED - For everything! For testing, for keeping me mapping and for just being there when I needed you.
Ryan S. - For being such a big help when I got problems. ;)
copy-mark - For giving me advices.
SolidSurf - At your Forum I will always find someone who's helping me :)

I hope everybody enjoys this map, I spent a lot of time working on it and also had a lot of fun as well :P. You may think part of the surf is unfinished but it's just invisible :) , also it definitely is not impossible. The map has a lot of secrets and a lot of different ways to unlock doors and find secrets, It really makes you think.

This is a surf skill map.
There are 3 levels. The first level is easy, 2nd is harder and 3 is really hard.
There is a time limit of 2 minutes, then everyone gets tele to jail. If you make it to the end, you get a ak.

Best results for:
sv_airaccelerate 100 - 200

Note: This is my first surf map that i used lighting, so if you are wondering why its so dark in some areas, thats pretty much why.
Enjoy!

A term that means nothing!

This map was created with skill and only skill in mind,
You don't have to learn each level as they are all similar.
Every level gets harder as you go on and it can get very hard towards the end.
There is a fun jail and you don't have to complete the surf to win. You get more of an advantage if you complete more of the surf, though!
Custom textures by Lody Blokady
Song used in 'Hale + Guu' track title is 'Love Tropicana'.

If you find a bug, pm me with a screenshot if you can. If I get a major bug or lots of little ones I may release a revised version.

Please don't rate unfairly if you have not played the map or find it to hard! It is designed for pro's!

This map was ported by ksf. The original creator is Serz.  I decided to upload it for people who want to play the map in source or momentum-mod and also because I couldn't find it online.  Here is the description of the csgo version (you don't need to install any plugins or scripts those instructions are for csgo):
hey so this is a surf map with 6 stages, it has fluid gameplay throug out the map (mostly) wich means if you fail you'll start back up at the last checkpoint with enough speed to finish that stage. 

also if you want to play the map as it is intended (please do) then install the SM plugin I included in the .rar, it's a particle precacher, 2 files big the smx and sp, merge the sourcemod folders and you should be good to go.

Big thanks to tony for geting me this after i tirelessly tried working stuff out with what i had from before. 

zone trigger_multiple's and teleport destinations for those of you with those kinds of server plugins;

stage1 - teleport1

stage2 - surfpart2.2blackbox

stage3 - surfpart2.3blackbox

stage4 - wtf

stage5 - wtf2

stage6 - surfpart2.zblackbox

endzone

bonus_start - poolbonus

bonus_end

This is my first surf map and everyone should try it.

First of this map is real danger zone and unlike most of the surf maps you are an easy target almost anywhere.

And because there is lots of weapons and enemy players seeking for you, its pretty hard to stay alive, but one good way to survive is to get better guns and try to shoot your enemies... pretty simple heh, NO!

But if you arent good surfer its not a problem, because jail is also good place to get frags and weapons. Just hope there is more teammates than enemies!

Try to make your own strategies, for both teams and you most likely handle this map well, but just remember to watch out for enemy rushers, campers, backtabbers, snipers etc..

Now download this map and kill those b*stards!
> Nice
